Introduction

Unnies was a special project girl group formed by the South Korean variety show Sister's Slam Dunk. The group was formed in order to accomplish cast member Min Hyo Rin's dream of debuting as a member of a girl group. Season 2 of the show was formatted to focus on a girl group project.
